name: David Müllerchen
bio: David Muellerchen is an Angular consultant and trainer. David has a passion: sharing knowledge. He loves to speak and teach at meetups and conferences. He is Also an organizer of the Hamburg Angular Meetup, NG-DE and a GDE in Angular.

name: Markus Wolf
bio: Markus Wolf is senior solution architect at XING. Since a few years he's deeply into frontend development, architectures and testing.

name: Nikolaus Rademacher
bio: As a child, Nik was interested in complex traffic infrastructures. Airports, radial highways and big interjections need to handle daily traffic, quickly guiding each person to their destination. Today, as a frontend web developer, he likes to build digital junctions.
